{"id": "1408817764054994955", "channel_id": "1400749543288475770", "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "content": "Update to the kath team, now more consistent and realistic.\n- Rat\nHere to rouse and exalt for massive crit rate and crit damage buff. Equipped with pizza and wheel to best support that. \n- clem\nUse strike for passive str income and debuff.\n- tawil\nIf you have lv12 tawil aliemus talent then you could free up some space here. This tawil build is a anti rng build, it gets exalt turn 1. The goal is to reroll turn one until you start with horla 2 cost. Fear tawil will increase all str gains. \nWhy tawil not horla? Cuz tawil has better stats and wing 4. Tawil functions as support and sub tank, pulling all sustain cards from exalt. \n- kath\nBehold Castor 2.0. This baddie shields a lot and gains a shit ton of aliemus in the process. Instead of setting up one big X burst with 50 combust, you should burst often with rat and clem exalt if you can. This is to farm the 2 arithmetica from building 10 combust \n- posse\nTeams lacks weakness and vulnerability so yeah.\n- rouse order\nKath - > rat then maybe clem\nTawil has no skey here so rouse doesn't do much", "timestamp": "2025-08-23T14:18:49.519000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1408817763891413212", "filename": "Screenshot_20250823_220342_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160547, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400749543288475770/1408817763891413212/Screenshot_20250823_220342_Morimens.jpg?ex=6a36a149&is=6a354fc9&hm=93c87a6894c36aac4c2c495242fbb5106a66d2a5cccfaf9e91ae858c7db858ec&"}]}
